    <!-- Application Structure Plan: The infographic is a single-page, scrollable narrative. It starts with a Hero section stating the mission. It then defines 'El Problema' using large, impactful stats. 'Nuestra Soluci√≥n: Haui' explains the product visually. 'El Modelo de Negocio' uses a simple diagram to show the two-sided market. 'Mercado Potencial' uses a bar chart to show the massive B2C user base. 'Proyecciones Financieras' uses a line chart to visualize the 5-year revenue goal. 'Impacto Clim√°tico y Social' uses donut charts and stats to quantify the positive effects. This structure tells a compelling story from problem to impact, making complex business data digestible and engaging for potential investors and partners. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices:
    - Problem Section: Goal: Inform. Viz: Large text numbers for impact. Justification: Highlighting key pain points (low income, high costs) with stark figures is highly effective. Method: Styled HTML.
    - Solution Section: Goal: Organize. Viz: Flowchart-like diagram. Justification: A visual flow best explains how the AI assistant works for the producer. Method: Structured HTML/CSS with Tailwind. NO SVG/Mermaid.
    - Business Model: Goal: Organize. Viz: Two-sided market diagram. Justification: Clearly shows the value exchange between B2C users and B2B customers. Method: Structured HTML/CSS with Tailwind.
    - Market Size: Goal: Compare. Viz: Bar Chart. Justification: Compares the number of producers in Colombia vs. LATAM, showing the scale of the opportunity. Library: Chart.js/Canvas.
    - Financial Projections: Goal: Change. Viz: Line Chart. Justification: Shows revenue growth over 5 years, a standard and clear way to present financial forecasts. Library: Chart.js/Canvas.
    - Impact Section: Goal: Inform/Compare. Viz: Donut Charts & Big Numbers. Justification: Donut charts effectively show proportional goals (e.g., % reduction in emissions), while big numbers highlight key social targets. Library: Chart.js/Canvas.
    -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
